org.jhotdraw.draw
Class AttributeKey<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.jhotdraw.draw.AttributeKey<T>

public class AttributeKey<T>
extends java.lang.Object

Provides typesafe getter and setter for a Figure attribute. An AttributeKey has a name, a type and a default value. The default value is returned by Figure.getAttribute, if a Figure does not have an attribute of the specified key.
